{"website": "http://web.archive.org/web/20201030082820id_/https://www.kroger.com/health/pharmacy/covid-care", "text": "\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--Kroger - Covid-19 Antibody Testing Locations--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--Skip to content--sep--Purchase History--sep--Digital Coupons--sep--Weekly Ad--sep--Shopping List--sep--Find a Store--sep--Payment Cards--sep--Gift Cards--sep--Sign In--sep--Popular--sep--Digital Coupons--sep--Weekly Ad--sep--Digital Coupon Event--sep--Ship to Home \u2013 NEW! Items--sep--My Prescriptions--sep--Departments--sep--Holiday Gift Guide--sep--Halloween--sep--Candy--sep--Game Day--sep--Fall Flavors--sep--Meat--sep--Fresh Fruit and Vegetables--sep--Pantry--sep--Frozen--sep--Beer, Wine and Liquor--sep--Seafood--sep--Dairy and Eggs--sep--Natural and Organic--sep--Deli--sep--Bakery--sep--Breakfast--sep--Beverages--sep--Home and Electronics--sep--Cleaning and Household--sep--Health and Wellness--sep--Vitamins and Supplements--sep--Personal Care--sep--Beauty--sep--Pet--sep--Floral--sep--Baby--sep--Ship to Home--sep--Specialty Diets--sep--International Cuisine--sep--Fred Meyer Jewelers--sep--Savings--sep--Planning--sep--Our Brands--sep--Discover--sep--Pharmacy and Health--sep--Payments and Services--sep--Search--sep--Clear--sep--Ship to--sep--\u00a0--sep--94102--sep-- --sep--Sign in--sep--Cart--sep-- Did you Know? Kroger Health is the first retail pharmacy to offer this service.--sep--Kroger Health\u2019s Rapid Antibody Test can provide critical information about past infection to patients who believe they may have previously been exposed to the coronavirus but were unable to access testing at the time of their potential infection. The point-of-care immunoassay validation studies showed, with a high degree of accuracy, whether or not an individual has established an adaptive immune response to SARS-CoV-2.--sep--This service is now available at Kroger\u2019s family of pharmacies in California and Michigan and will be available at Kroger\u2019s pharmacies and clinics in 35 states as soon as November.--sep--What You Need to Know Before Scheduling:--sep--Eligibility: --sep--Antibody Testing is currently available at Kroger\u2019s family of pharmacies in California and Michigan. Testing will be available across all pharmacies and clinics as soon as November. Individuals who believe they may have already been infected with COVID-19 and are not currently experiencing symptoms are eligible for the test.--sep--Cost:--sep--The tests, which are supplied by Whitmire Medical, are available to our customers for $25.--sep--Schedule: --sep--California and Michigan patients may call 1-888-837-8852 to schedule an appointment.--sep--Results: --sep--Testing involves a blood-based fingerstick test and results are available within 15 minutes.--sep--We\u2019re Committed to You.--sep--Each and every day, Kroger Health is taking extra steps to ensure the health and safety of our customers and communities. Find out how.--sep--Keep on Exploring Health & Wellness--sep-- --sep--ABOUT THE COMPANY--sep--About the Company--sep--Advertise With Us--sep--Careers--sep--Community--sep--Express HR--sep--Investor Relations--sep--Kroger Real Estate--sep--News Room--sep--Vendors & Suppliers--sep--COMMUNITY--sep--Kroger Community Rewards--sep--Honoring Our Heroes--sep--Sustainability--sep--Request a Donation--sep--CUSTOMER SERVICE--sep--Help--sep--FAQs--sep--Contact Us--sep--Customer Comments--sep--Digital Coupons Policy--sep--My Prescriptions FAQs--sep--Recall Alerts--sep--Feedback--sep--SERVICES--sep--Deli/Bakery Ordering--sep--Digital Coupons--sep--Gift Cards--sep--Mobile App--sep--Receipt Survey Invitation--sep--Recipes--sep--Shopping List--s