{"website": "http://web.archive.org/web/20200531225954id_/https://www.kroger.com/i/coronavirus-update/store-safety", "text": "\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--Kroger - Store Safety Measures & Information - Coronavirus Update--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--\n--sep--Skip to content--sep--Sign In--sep--Popular--sep--Buy 5, Save $1 Each--sep--Ways to Shop--sep--Weekly Ad--sep--Digital Coupons--sep--My Prescriptions--sep--Departments--sep--Summer Shop--sep--At Home--sep--Father's Day Shop--sep--Graduation Shop--sep--Meat and Seafood--sep--Fresh Fruit and Vegetables--sep--Pantry--sep--Natural and Organic--sep--Dairy and Eggs--sep--Floral--sep--Frozen--sep--Deli--sep--Bakery--sep--Beer, Wine and Liquor--sep--Candy--sep--Home and Electronics--sep--Cleaning and Household--sep--Health and Wellness--sep--Beauty--sep--Personal Care--sep--Vitamins and Supplements--sep--Baby--sep--Pet--sep--Ship to Home--sep--Specialty Diets--sep--International Cuisine--sep--Fred Meyer Jewelers--sep--Savings--sep--Shop by Brand--sep--Discover--sep--Pharmacy and Health--sep--Money and Perks--sep--Search--sep--Clear--sep--Ship to--sep--\u00a0--sep--95050--sep-- --sep--Locations--sep--Sign In--sep--Cart--sep--Gift Cards--sep--Lists--sep--Weekly Ad--sep--Digital Coupons--sep--Our Payment Cards--sep--Help--sep--We want you to feel comfortable every time you walk through our doors. Each and every day, we\u2019re taking extra steps to ensure the health and safety of our customers and communities.--sep-- --sep--\u00a0--sep--We are adjusting some store operating hours based on local circumstances. We will continue to make decisions that allow us to operate clean, open and stocked stores to serve our communities.--sep--See Store Hours--sep-- --sep-- --sep-- --sep--\u00a0--sep--Due to the current COVID-19 pandemic, we are temporarily suspending product returns on Food products, Cosmetics & Apparel (clothing, shoes & accessories).--sep--View Policy--sep-- --sep-- --sep--\u00a0--sep--Our pharmacy drive thru and walk-up services remain operational and staffed to meet your needs. Find Pharmacy hours, service information and more.--sep-- --sep--View Hours & Services--sep-- --sep-- --sep--\u00a0--sep--The Little Clinic remains dedicated to providing customer-focused health care to our communities. Get the latest updates on our services, including virtual care options.--sep--See Clinic Updates--sep-- --sep-- --sep--Store Information & Safety Measures--sep--March Fuel Points Rollover--sep--When You\u2019re Ready to Refuel, We\u2019ve Got You Covered. We\u2019re all driving a little less right now, and we know you might need some extra time to use your fuel points. We\u2019re with you. On May 2, any unused March fuel points will be added to your April balance and won\u2019t expire until the end of May. --sep--Learn more--sep--. --sep--Fee-Free Government Check Cashing--sep--Beginning April 29, you can take advantage of fee-free check cashing on any government paper check. Limited time only. Restrictions apply, see associate for details. --sep--Learn More--sep--.--sep--Customer Capacity Limits--sep--Beginning April 7, The Kroger Co. will begin to limit the number of customers to 50% capacity to allow for proper physical distancing in every store. --sep--Read the full press release here--sep-- and --sep--read related FAQs here--sep--.--sep--Cleaning and Disinfecting--sep--All stores are following enhanced cleaning and disinfecting protocols that includes cleaning commonly used areas and wiping down equipment and high-touch surfaces.--sep--Protective Barriers--sep--We\u2019re installing protective barriers at check lanes and Pharmacy counters (as well as The Little Clinic and Starbucks) to protect both customers and associates.--sep--Social Distancing--sep--As part of our efforts to keep you safe and to encourage social distancing, you may notice signage or floor markers at some locations that encourage proper physical distance between yourself and other shoppers.--sep--Exclusive Shopping Hours for Higher-Risk Customers--sep--Please save the earliest shopping times, usually 6-8am, for senior shoppers and higher-risk customers, as described by the CDC. Check your store for more details.--sep--Free Pickup--sep--Due to increased demand, you may experience longer wait times, limited inventory, limited pickup time slots or delayed deliveries. Our associates are working around the clock to make it easier for you to get what you need. In the meantime, we invite you to try our FREE pickup service at a store near you.--sep--SNAP EBT Payment Option for Pickup--sep--As part of our fresh for everyone commitment, we are now accepting SNAP EBT payments for pickup at all pickup locations. --sep--Quick Links--sep--Main Page--sep--Learn More--sep--Learn More--sep--View Past Messages--sep--See How We\u2019re Supporting Communities with Hunger Relief--sep--Last Updated: Tuesday, April 28, 2020--sep-- --sep--Connect With Us:--sep--Download the App:--sep--ABOUT THE COMPANY--sep--About the Company--sep--Advertise With Us--sep--Careers--sep--Community--sep--Express HR--sep--Investor Relations--sep--Kroger Real Estate--sep--News Room--sep--Vendors & Suppliers--sep--COMMUNITY--sep--Kroger Community Rewards--sep--Honoring Our Heroes--sep--Sustainability--sep--Request a Donation--sep--CUSTOMER SERVICE--sep--FAQs--sep--Contact Us--sep--Customer Comments--sep--Digital Coupons Policy--sep--My Prescriptions FAQs--sep--Recall Alerts--sep--Feedback--sep--SERVICES--sep--Deli/Bakery Ordering--sep--Digital Coupons--sep--Gift Card Mall--sep--Join Our Customer Panel--sep--Mobile App--sep--Receipt Survey Invitation--sep--Recipes--sep--Shopping List--sep--Store Locator--sep--Weekly Ad--sep--M